## Professional Background

Freelance 2D artist since 2019, pixel art specialist since 2020.
750+ completed orders across platforms.
500+ reviews, 99% five-star satisfaction.

### Platforms

- **Fiverr** (@marwanhasnaoui) — 447 reviews, 4.9 rating, $30/hr listed
- **Twine** (twine.net) — 2D Animator, Character Designer, Concept Artist, Graphic Designer, Illustrator

### Skills

- **Expert:** Photoshop, Character Design, Illustrator, 2D Animation, Clip Studio Paint, Procreate
- **Intermediate:** Blender, UI design, 3D modeling
- **Industries:** Gaming, Media/Entertainment, Software

His technical range is broader than Fiverr suggests —
Illustrator, Blender, and UI work don't appear in Fiverr listings.

### Notable Prior Work

Dogs of Elon NFT collection (Jun–Oct 2021).
Earned over 5 ETH on OpenSea.
He told Evan directly he could contribute to NFT minting
if OIS pursues that path.

### Typical Fiverr Work

Small-to-medium pixel art commissions ($10–$200 range):
NFT art, stream avatars, character sprites, animations.
Repeat clients praise communication, speed, detail attention,
and willingness to revise without complaint.
The OIS engagement is by far his most complex
and longest-running project visible publicly.

