## Contract Status

- **Document:** Creative Services Agreement
- **Parties:** Outside Inn Studios, LLC × Marwan Hasnaoui
- **Revised Draft:** February 25, 2026
- **DocuSign ID:** `EEB8114E-C55D-4B8D-8A96-075075DF5A91`
- **Signed by Evan:** Feb 25, 2026
- **Signed by Marwan:** Pending
- **Supersedes:** NDA signed Oct 20, 2025
- **Governing law:** State of New York

### Contract Sections

**§1 Parties.**
Client: Outside Inn Studios, LLC (Evan Werner).
Artist: Marwan Hasnaoui.

**§2 Prior Payments.**
11 payments totaling $2,291.17.
Final, non-refundable, not subject to dispute.

**§3 Logo Closeout & Holdt Portrait.**
Original logo/wordmark scope concluded.
Remaining $250 reallocated to Holdt character portrait
optimized for logo/wordmark sizing
(favicon, channel ID, scalable brand mark).
Requires all sizing formats + layered source files.
Fee: $250.00.

**§4a Animation Completion.**
$500 Part 1 already paid.
Completion fee: $500.00.
Delivery requires:
optimized exports for stream use,
underlying video in highest quality,
minimum one still frame for poster production,
all source project files in native format.

**§4b Animation Polish.**
Minor refinements only:
color adjustments, timing tweaks,
smoothness, small fixes.
Excludes new scenes, structural changes,
style changes, reanimation.
Capped at 3 revision rounds.
Beyond that billed separately.
Fee: $250.00.

**§5 Stream Alerts Pack.**
New Scrivener alert + New Keeper alert.
All export formats + source files.
Fee: $150.00.

**§6 Acceptance & Payment.**
USD or agreed crypto (Solana or equivalent).
7 business day acceptance window
(deemed accepted if no response).
Payment within 5 business days of acceptance.
Schedule: $250 → $500 → $250 → $150.

**§7 Merchandise Royalty.**
$0.77/unit on all merch featuring his artwork.
No amendment needed per product type.
"Net unit sold" excludes returns, refunds,
chargebacks, damaged goods, samples,
giveaways, influencer units, internal use.
Quarterly reporting.
Payout at $497.70 threshold,
within 30 days of quarter end.
Lifetime cap: $7,700.00.
Term: 14 years.
Ceases on cap or term, whichever first.

**§8 Artist Signature & Portfolio.**
May provide signature file for merch
(placement at EIW discretion).
Portfolio rights post-public release
without additional permission.

**§9 Intellectual Property.**
Work-for-hire.
All rights vest in OIS upon full payment.
Backup irrevocable assignment clause.
All source/working files delivered upon payment.
No rights retained except §8.

**§10 Representations & Indemnification.**
All work original.
No third-party IP infringement.
No undisclosed third-party assets.
Indemnifies OIS against claims from breach.

**§11 Independent Contractor.**
No partnership, joint venture,
employment, or profit-sharing.

**§12 Confidentiality.**
All project details confidential.
No disclosure without prior written consent.

**§13 Dispute Resolution.**
Good-faith negotiation (30 days).
Then binding arbitration (AAA rules),
remote or Westchester County, NY.
Royalty claims within 2 years of relevant quarter.

**§14 Term & Termination.**
Effective upon signing through completion.
EIW may terminate uncommenced deliverables
with 7 days notice.
In-progress work compensated pro-rata.
Surviving: §7, §8, §9, §10, §12, §13.

**§15 General.**
Entire agreement. Amendments in writing only.

